### 1️⃣ Register new user request
POST http://localhost:8080/register/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sasidhar K",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "mobile": "9999999999",
  "message": "Please add me as a new user."
}

### 2️⃣ Admin login (use credentials from DataInitializer)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": {ADMIN_EMAIL},
  "password": {ADMIN_PASSWORD}
}

### 3️⃣ Get pending registration requests
GET http://localhost:8080/register/admin/pending
Authorization: Bearer <paste_token_here>

### 4️⃣ Approve a registration request
POST http://localhost:8080/register/admin/approve/1
Authorization: Bearer <paste_token_here>

### 5️⃣ User login after approval
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "User@1234"
}

### 6️⃣ View recharge plans
GET http://localhost:8080/plans

### 7️⃣ Perform a recharge
POST http://localhost:8080/recharge?userId=1&planId=2&paymentMethod=UPI
Authorization: Bearer <paste_user_token_here>

### 8️⃣ Check user recharge history
GET http://localhost:8080/recharge/history/1
Authorization: Bearer <paste_user_token_here>

### 9️⃣ Send delete account request
POST http://localhost:8080/user/requests/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "reason": "I want to delete my account."
}
